name: Throbbing Semi-SMOL Pixelzoom
description: Tried to the best of my ability to reproduce the likeness of Avery Famous, instigator of the SMOL NFT micro artwork movement that started early June 2021. As this file is of variable resolution, it only qualifies as a legitimate authorized SMOL piece during half of its 16 frames of animation, constituting thus a fork of the main movement. Originally released 6 June 2021 as OBJKT 117989 on HeN.
